#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:26
msgid ""
"Choose the interface language. After saving, the selected language takes "
"precedence over the browser language."
msgstr "选择界面语言。保存后，所选语言将优先于浏览器语言。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:31
msgid "Profile"
msgstr "个人资料"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:38
msgid "Theme"
msgstr "主题"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:41
msgid ""
"Choose a light or dark theme, or automatically follow your system setting."
msgstr "手动选择明暗主题，或基于系统设置自动切换。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:45
msgid "Bookmark date format"
msgstr "书签日期格式"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:48
msgid ""
"Show bookmark dates as relative dates, absolute dates, or hide them entirely."
msgstr "书签日期显示为相对日期、绝对日期，或隐藏。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:52
msgid "Bookmark description"
msgstr "书签描述"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:55
msgid ""
"Show bookmark descriptions and tags in one line, or render them in separate "
"blocks."
msgstr "书签描述与标签同行显示，或另起分块显示。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:59
msgid "Bookmark description max lines"
msgstr "书签描述最大行数"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:62
msgid "Limit how many lines are shown for bookmark descriptions."
msgstr "限制书签描述显示的最大行数。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:68
msgid "Show bookmark URL"
msgstr "显示书签 URL"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:71
msgid "Display the bookmark URL below the title."
msgstr "在书签标题下显示书签 URL。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:77
msgid "Show notes permanently"
msgstr "永久显示笔记"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:80
msgid "Keep notes expanded by default instead of toggling them individually."
msgstr "默认展开笔记，而不是逐条手动切换。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:81
msgid "You can also temporarily show all notes with the keyboard shortcut"
msgstr "你也可以通过键盘快捷键临时显示全部笔记"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:85
msgid "Bookmark actions"
msgstr "书签动作"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:103
msgid "Choose which actions are shown for each bookmark."
msgstr "选择每条书签要显示的动作。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:107
msgid "Open bookmarks in"
msgstr "书签打开方式"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:110
msgid "Open bookmarks in the current page or in a new page."
msgstr "在当前页面或新页面中打开书签。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:114
msgid "Items per page"
msgstr "每页书签数量"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:122
msgid "Choose how many bookmarks are shown on each page."
msgstr "选择每页显示多少条书签。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:128
msgid "Sticky search bar"
msgstr "粘性搜索栏"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:131
msgid "Keep the search and action controls pinned to the top while you scroll."
msgstr "滚动时将搜索栏和操作区固定在顶部。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:137
msgid "Sticky pagination"
msgstr "粘性分页"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:140
msgid "Keep the pagination controls pinned to the bottom while you scroll."
msgstr "滚动时将分页控件固定在底部。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:146
msgid "Sticky side panel"
msgstr "侧边栏跟随"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:149
msgid "Keep the side panel visible while scrolling on wider screens."
msgstr "在较宽屏幕上滚动时保持侧边栏可见。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:150
msgid "This option is automatically disabled when the side panel is collapsed."
msgstr "当侧边栏折叠时，此选项会自动禁用。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:156
msgid "Collapse side panel"
msgstr "折叠侧边栏"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:159
msgid "Collapse the side panel by default to give the bookmark list more room."
msgstr "默认折叠侧边栏，为书签列表留出更多空间。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:165
msgid "Hide bundles"
msgstr "隐藏过滤器"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:168
msgid "Hide the bundles panel in the sidebar if you do not use bundles."
msgstr "如果你不使用过滤器，可在侧边栏中隐藏过滤器面板。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:172
msgid "Tag search"
msgstr "标签搜索"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:175
msgid "In strict mode, tags must be prefixed with a hash character (#)."
msgstr "在严格模式下，标签必须带有井号前缀（#）。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:176
msgid "In lax mode, tags can also be found without the hash character."
msgstr "在宽松模式下，没有“#”前缀的标签也能被搜索到。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:177
msgid ""
"Without the hash character, tags are harder to distinguish from ordinary "
"search terms, so unrelated results may also match."
msgstr "如果没有井号前缀，标签与普通关键词更难区分，因此也可能匹配到无关结果。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:181
msgid "Tag grouping"
msgstr "标签聚合"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:184
msgid "In alphabetical mode, tags are grouped by the first letter."
msgstr "在 首字母 模式下，标签会按首字母分组。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:185
msgid "If disabled, tags are shown without grouping."
msgstr "关闭后，标签将不进行分组显示。"

msgid "This setting applies to the Tags module in the sidebar."
msgstr "此设置仅作用于侧边栏中的标签模块。"

msgid "Enable the Tags module in Sidebar modules to configure this setting."
msgstr "请先在“侧边栏模块”中启用“标签”模块，再配置此设置。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:191
#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:193
msgid "Auto Tagging"
msgstr "自动标签"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:199
msgid "Automatically add tags to bookmarks based on custom rules."
msgstr "根据自定义规则为书签自动添加标签。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:200
msgid "Each line is one rule that maps a URL to one or more tags. For example:"
msgstr "每行是一条规则，将 URL 映射到一个或多个标签。例如："

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:208
msgid "Enable Favicons"
msgstr "启用 Favicons"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:211
msgid ""
"Automatically load favicons for bookmarked websites and display them next to "
"each bookmark."
msgstr "自动为已收藏的网站加载 favicon，并显示在每条书签旁边。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:212
msgid "Enabling this feature downloads all missing favicons in the background."
msgstr "启用后会在后台下载所有缺失的 favicon。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:213
msgid "By default, this feature uses a Google service to fetch favicons."
msgstr "默认情况下，此功能使用 Google 的服务获取 favicon。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:214
msgid "If you prefer a different provider, check the"
msgstr "如果你更喜欢其他提供方，请查看"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:214
msgid "options documentation"
msgstr "配置文档"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:217
msgid "Refresh Favicons"
msgstr "刷新 Favicons"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:223
msgid "Enable Preview Images"
msgstr "启用预览图"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:226
msgid ""
"Automatically load preview images for bookmarked websites and display them "
"next to each bookmark."
msgstr "自动为已收藏的网站加载预览图，并显示在每条书签旁边。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:227
msgid ""
"Enabling this feature downloads missing preview images in the background."
msgstr "启用后会在后台下载缺失的预览图。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:231
msgid "Internet Archive integration"
msgstr "Internet Archive 集成"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:234
msgid ""
"When enabled, snapshots of bookmarked websites are automatically created on "
"the Internet Archive Wayback Machine."
msgstr ""
"启用后，会自动在 Internet Archive Wayback Machine 上为已收藏的网站创建快照。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:235
msgid "This helps preserve websites as they looked when you bookmarked them."
msgstr "这有助于保留网站在你收藏时的样貌。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:236
msgid ""
"Please consider supporting the Internet Archive if you rely on this feature."
msgstr "如果你依赖此功能，请考虑支持 Internet Archive。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:242
msgid "Enable bookmark sharing"
msgstr "启用书签分享"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:245
msgid ""
"Allow bookmarks to be shared with other users and allow viewing bookmarks "
"shared by others."
msgstr "允许将书签分享给其他用户，并允许查看其他人分享的书签。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:251
msgid "Enable public bookmark sharing"
msgstr "启用公开书签分享"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:254
msgid "Make shared bookmarks visible without requiring a login."
msgstr "无需登录即可查看已分享书签。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:255
msgid "Anyone who can access this instance can then browse the"
msgstr "任何可访问本实例的人随后都可以浏览"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:255
msgid "shared bookmarks page"
msgstr "已分享书签页面"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:262
msgid "Automatically create HTML snapshots"
msgstr "自动创建 HTML 快照"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:265
msgid "Automatically create HTML snapshots when adding new bookmarks."
msgstr "添加新书签时自动创建 HTML 快照。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:266
msgid ""
"If disabled, snapshots can still be created manually from the bookmark "
"details view."
msgstr "即使关闭，也仍可以在书签详情页手动创建快照。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:268
msgid "Create missing HTML snapshots"
msgstr "创建缺失的 HTML 快照"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:274
msgid "Create bookmarks as unread by default"
msgstr "默认将新书签标记为未读"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:277
msgid "Set newly created bookmarks to unread by default."
msgstr "默认将新建书签标记为未读。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:283
msgid "Create bookmarks as shared by default"
msgstr "默认将新书签标记为已分享"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:286
msgid "Set newly created bookmarks to shared by default."
msgstr "默认将新建书签标记为已分享。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:292
#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:294
msgid "Custom CSS"
msgstr "自定义 CSS"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:300
msgid "Add custom CSS that is loaded for your profile."
msgstr "为你的个人配置添加自定义 CSS。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:306
#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:308
msgid "Custom domain normalization"
msgstr "自定义域名归一化"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:314
msgid "Configure one root domain per line."
msgstr "每行配置一个根域名。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:315
msgid ""
"All matching subdomains are normalized to the configured root domain, which "
"affects favicon-based domain filters."
msgstr ""
"所有匹配的子域名都会归一化为所配置的根域名，这会影响基于 favicon 的域名筛选。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:316
msgid ""
"Example: setting example.com normalizes a.example.com and b.example.com to "
"example.com."
msgstr ""
"例如：设置 example.com 后，a.example.com 和 b.example.com 会被归一化为 "
"example.com。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:317
msgid ""
"If you also set a.example.com explicitly, that subdomain remains separate "
"while other subdomains still normalize to example.com."
msgstr ""
"如果你同时显式设置 a.example.com，那么该子域名会保持独立，其他子域名仍会归一"
"化为 example.com。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:328
msgid "Global settings"
msgstr "全局设置"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:332
msgid "Landing page"
msgstr "默认首页"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:335
msgid ""
"Choose which page unauthenticated users are redirected to when they open the "
"root URL."
msgstr "选择未登录用户打开根路径时将被重定向到哪个页面。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:339
msgid "Guest user profile"
msgstr "访客用户配置"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:342
msgid ""
"Choose which profile is used for anonymous visitors viewing publicly shared "
"bookmarks."
msgstr "选择匿名访客查看公开分享书签时使用的用户配置。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:348
msgid "Enable hover prefetching for internal links"
msgstr "启用内部链接悬停预取"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:351
msgid ""
"Prefetch internal links when users hover over them. This improves perceived "
"speed, but increases server load."
msgstr ""
"用户悬停在内部链接上时预取目标页面。这样可以提升体感速度，但也会增加服务器负"
"载。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/general.html:363
